snippet: Davey Johnson will return as the Washington Nationals’ manager for one more year and then become a consultant to the club in 2014.
abstract: Washington Nationals retain manager Davey Johnson for 2013 season; other MLB news noted.
lead_paragraph: Davey Johnson will return as the Washington Nationals’ manager for one more year and then become a consultant to the club in 2014.
